{"tid":20743,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"依家仲有冇人仍然支持青年新政","createTime":"2016-12-03T13:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:50:46.000Z","uid":43785,"like":35,"dislike":144,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b6b5a2d9a80f310e2a62f7586c5d30ec67341455","tid":20743,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"零戰功，不斷影衰本土派，<br />\n生又累人，死又累街坊。<br />\n搞到眾叛親離，人人跳船，<br />\n高登第一支持者林浩基寧願話自己返工都唔去<br />\n<br />\n講下大家仲用乜野理由去呃自己支持青年新政<br />\n我都好想支持青年新政。<br />\n<br />\n佢地呢幾個月，柒到連自己都說服唔到自己，點解要支持你。<br />\n有冇人可以講自己仍然支持青政理由係乜。"},{"pid":"81569fcd8dccffe0c3d1015b11ae0dd8587d9565","tid":20743,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"遊bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc641f953edcc04f2796577bb21a3663270b5bd","tid":20743,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f55fbb93867bf9ba8c256178aa1bc5d275c0750","tid":20743,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"而家重支持佢地果班衰D講句分分鐘庇護工場都唔收&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b144449e1e748f50be3a7f5003e8395526bff4","tid":20743,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"有時d野唔係本土分化唔分化問題<br />\n係佢地根本連自己做緊乜都唔知<br />\n<br />\n當初講資源論，講入左去先既又係佢，<br />\n依家入去又玩野，入唔到去一蚊都冇<br />\n咁即係點呀，一時一樣。<br />\n<br />\n又話為香港無底線抗爭，搞時代革命，又去左邊呀<br />\n<br />\n我俾左票你，你依家一次又一次呃我，想點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係支持唔落啦"},{"pid":"2252540710d36784e91f7b66d9c2146cc8f7077f","tid":20743,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家重支持佢地果班衰D講句分分鐘